  "detailed_description": "<strong>Enionax</strong> is sent back to 1980 — the dawning of video games — due to a mistake.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A classic plateformer 2D game</h2>Help her come back to <strong>our time</strong> by going through the various levels/eras of platformers.<br>You will have to walk through various supports to come back to our time in this <strong>platefomer 2D game</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725470/extras/a439962909fb13b15ed07801e31a9ad1.poster.avif?t=1671058422\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725470/extras/a439962909fb13b15ed07801e31a9ad1.webm?t=1671058422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725470/extras/a439962909fb13b15ed07801e31a9ad1.mp4?t=1671058422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Assets</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A classic plateformer 2D game !<br></li><li>Revisit the various eras of video games with humour.<br></li><li>Try to find out all the easter eggs in the game.<br></li><li>Go through various gameplays as times change.<br></li><li>Enjoy original music by Valentin Skorra.</li></ul>",
